data.description: This 1338 square foot townhome home has 2 bedrooms and 3.0 bathrooms. This home is located at 4863 W Daybreak Pkwy, South Jordan, UT 84009.
data.whatILove: Beautiful row end town-home within walking distance of SoDa Row, UofU hospital, and Trax. As a Daybreak resident you'll have access to a fitness center, tennis courts, basketball courts, free kayak rentals, swimming pools, included internet access. If you are looking for an amazing home this is the one! 9 foot ceilings on main floor. Upgraded with granite counter-tops, stainless steel kitchen sink, subway tile backslash, modern industrial lighting in kitchen, over $2,000 of audio speakers throughout entire house including surround sound in the living room installed by the builder, security cameras on the entrances with mobile viewing, central vacuum, two tone paint through out, pallet wall in master bedroom, and all appliances included!
